date-calc: Date::Calc (Perl module)
date-calc:
date-calc: This package consists of a C library (intended to make life
date-calc: easier for C developers) and a Perl module to access this
date-calc: library from Perl.
date-calc: 
date-calc: The library provides all sorts of date calculations based on
date-calc: the Gregorian calendar (the one used in all western countries
date-calc: today), thereby complying with all relevant norms and standards:
date-calc: ISO/R 2015-1971, DIN 1355 and, to some extent, ISO 8601 (where
date-calc: applicable).
